
Note:
 This source currently only compiles and runs on Mac OS X. An attempt was made to port the earlier 
XForms-based QSplat code to wxWindows, unifying the source and creating a single Makefile. This process 
was never completed.

To make and install wxWindows for Mac OS X:
mkdir wxdev
cd wxdev
cvs -d:pserver:anoncvs@cvs.wxwindows.org:/home/wxcvs checkout wxWindows
cd wxWindows
mkdir build
cd build
../configure --with-opengl --disable-shared --enable-no_rtti
make
   If desired, edit Makefile and change the "prefix" variable to wherever 
  you would like wxWindows installed.
make install

